<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 27 at 7:27AM EST  by NWS Cleveland</headline>
<description>Currently getting some quick bursts of snow this morning, and
while the stronger echoes on radar should be moving out soon,
light snow will continue to be possible until temperatures climb
above freezing later this morning. Light accumulations are
possible. Drivers are urged to reduce speed where snow is
accumulating.</description>
